      <title>南非预算赤字扩大 令投资者失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/s-africa-budget-leaves-investors-cold-as-deficit-widens-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的预算更新显示，公共财政面临越来越大的压力，这加剧了新联合政府吸引更多投资进入该地区最大经济体的必要性。彭博新闻社的 Ntando Thukwana 与 Jennifer Zabasajja 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/s-africa-budget-leaves-investors-cold-as-deficit-widens-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 06:25:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士央行报告九个月盈利，因投资组合收益抵消法郎下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/snb-reports-nine-month-profit-as-portfolio-gains-offset-franc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行因股票、债券和黄金价格上涨而连续九个月获得稳健盈利，增加了其在两年中断后重新开始利润分配的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/snb-reports-nine-month-profit-as-portfolio-gains-offset-franc</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 06:21:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>百威英博销量因亚太地区销售不佳而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/anheuser-busch-volumes-fall-after-poor-sales-in-asia-pacific</link>
      <description><![CDATA[百威英博表示，由于中国和阿根廷市场销售持续疲软，其啤酒销量降幅超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/anheuser-busch-volumes-fall-after-poor-sales-in-asia-pacific</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 06:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
