    <item>
      <title>贷款逆风持续，法国巴黎银行从交易中获益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/bnp-paribas-gets-boost-from-trading-as-lending-headwinds-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于贷款业务继续受到阻力的困扰，法国巴黎银行依靠其投资银行和资产管理部门来提升第三季度的业绩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/bnp-paribas-gets-boost-from-trading-as-lending-headwinds-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 06:00:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行通胀目标在望但斗争尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ecb-inflation-goal-in-sight-but-fight-not-over-lagarde-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧元区消费者价格增长率正朝着欧洲央行 2% 的目标迈进，但这场斗争尚未胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ecb-inflation-goal-in-sight-but-fight-not-over-lagarde-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 05:59:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元兑美元上涨，因日本央行仍有可能再次加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/yen-stays-in-tight-range-vs-dollar-after-boj-holds-pat-on-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继日本央行维持利率不变之后，日元兑美元汇率在一周内首次上涨，市场关注今天下午行长上田和夫的新闻发布会，寻找未来加息的暗示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/yen-stays-in-tight-range-vs-dollar-after-boj-holds-pat-on-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台风康蕾袭击台湾，上海迎来暴雨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/taiwan-braces-for-super-typhoon-kong-rey-after-shutting-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台风康蕾携带危险大风登陆台湾，随着大型风暴朝中国大陆移动，上海将迎来自 1981 年以来 11 月份最强降雨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/taiwan-braces-for-super-typhoon-kong-rey-after-shutting-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:22:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车巨头之争中比亚迪销量首次超越特斯拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/byd-sales-beat-tesla-for-first-time-in-battle-of-ev-giants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国比亚迪股份有限公司公布季度营收，自两家公司在全球电动汽车销量上展开激烈竞争以来，首次超过特斯拉公司。彭博电视台的 Minmin Low 报道了这一消息。（视频中删除了数据错误的图表）（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/byd-sales-beat-tesla-for-first-time-in-battle-of-ev-giants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 00:17:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市下跌，日元走强，日本央行维持利率不变：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四亚洲股市下跌，因强劲的经济数据使美联储即将降息的前景变得模糊。日本央行公布利率决定后，日元走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 22:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
